    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been totally babied, kept tucked away in the garage, and it still feels brand new. Everything is pristine, runs like a dream, and is ready for a new home. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I just know you\u2019re going to adore driving it as much as I have. Come take a look\u2014it's even better in person!",
