      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and remains in showroom condition. The exterior features a factory-perfect finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights every aggressive line. Inside, the black Dakota leather with blue contrast stitching retains its original matte texture and fresh scent, free from any wear, creases, or odors. Mechanically, it is flawless; all service has been performed exclusively by authorized BMW technicians, with a comprehensive binder of records included. With low mileage and zero track time, this M2 drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Every electronic component, from the Harman Kardon surround sound to the driver assistance systems, functions perfectly. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
